1
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:39,960
Get up.

2
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,000
Get up.

3
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,240
Get up.

4
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,680
Get up.

5
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:51,960
Get up.

6
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,400
Get up.

7
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,520
Get up.

8
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,040
Get up.

9
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,400
I can't take it anymore.

10
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,480
Don't. I haven't had enough fun yet.

11
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,800
Who's next?

12
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:38,040
Shen Zhixia, did you see clearly?

13
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,760
Those who bullied you before,

14
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,680
I will get payback for you today.

15
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,920
All the grievances you've suffered,

16
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:44,380
and the beatings you took,

17
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:47,400
will never happen again from today on.

18
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:53,770
How did you know I was at the boxing gym?

19
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,770
Just passing by.

20
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,050
What a coincidence.

21
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,520
It really is.

22
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,440
When you were in the Shen family,

23
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,880
did you suffer a lot?

24
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:12,960
We're about to get a divorce.

25
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,160
Why ask this now?

26
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,600
Didn't you let Shen Jingyao

27
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,060
take them away yesterday?

28
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,579
I won't let you return to the Shen family.

29
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,740
At least with you here,

30
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,120
we can remind Su Manyun

31
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,960
that the Lu family doesn't take the surname Su.

32
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,420
Since we're on this topic,

33
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,360
let's put our cards on the table.

34
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,520
With this marriage,

35
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,250
no one cares if we want it or not.

36
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,520
Let's make an agreement.

37
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:43,960
Let's hear it.

38
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,320
First,

39
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,050
act like a couple in public,

40
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,840
but cross no lines in private.

41
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,640
Second,

42
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:51,720
no interference in each other's private lives.

43
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:52,520
Third,

44
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,440
whether you want to separate

45
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,960
or I want a breakup,

46
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:56,760
once it's brought up,

47
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,160
the marriage ends.

48
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,480
No pestering.

49
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,400
I have three conditions too.

50
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:07,920
First,

51
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,640
whether you return to the Shen family

52
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:11,480
or go anywhere dangerous,

53
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,080
I must accompany you.

54
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,640
Second,

55
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,360
no matter what happens,

56
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,760
you can ask me for help.

57
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,160
Don't shoulder it alone.

58
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,279
Third,

59
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,520
regarding each other's matters,

60
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,980
we must be open and honest.

61
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,610
No hiding anything.

62
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,440
Speak.

63
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,320
Mr. Lu,

64
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:38,520
the matter at the boxing gym is settled.

65
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,280
I got it.

66
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,570
What did you handle?

67
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:46,920
Nothing.

68
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:58,400
This boxing gym has been transferred to Mr. Lu's name.

69
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,520
Before opening tomorrow,

70
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:01,240
tell all these people to get lost.

71
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,520
Don't let them appear in front of our young madam again.

72
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,320
Yes.

73
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,890
All of you get out tomorrow.

74
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:22,000
I came here to find Shen Jingyao.

75
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:24,080
I didn't expect him to get away.

76
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,400
Why me?

77
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,960
Help me.

78
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:27,180
These letters were obviously returned.

79
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:29,680
Who was the original owner asking for help?

80
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,360
The person she corresponded with must know more.

81
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:34,600
They might even know who killed her.

82
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,760
But...

83
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:41,400
Who exactly is J?

84
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:43,480
Young Madam.

85
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:44,920
Come in.

86
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,640
Slow down.

87
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:49,100
Why are you in such a hurry?

88
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:52,240
It was the second young master.

89
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,800
He asked me to give this to you

90
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:56,080
and told me not to let anyone else see it.

91
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,080
Look at this.

92
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,480
Lu Jingxi.

93
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,210
What does he want this time?

94
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,720
He's asking me out to dinner.

95
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,800
Tell him to get lost.

96
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,600
Yes.

97
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,280
Wait.

98
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,200
Could it be

99
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:37,820
that he was the one corresponding with the original owner?

100
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,720
Hello. Welcome.

101
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,200
Hello.

102
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:54,720
Hello.

103
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:57,200
How may I help you?

104
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,450
Sister-in-law.

105
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,160
Second Young Master invited me here

106
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,760
not just for a meal, right?

107
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,960
The Lu family's dining table

108
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:16,400
is much livelier than this.

109
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:18,770
Actually, inviting you here today

110
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,530
isn't for anything urgent.

111
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,000
I just feel

112
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:24,240
there are some misunderstandings between us

113
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,970
and we need to sit down and talk.

114
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,010
Talk about the past,

115
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,930
and also the future.

116
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:32,320
Then let's talk about the past first.

117
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:36,770
What does the past look like to you, Second Young Master?

118
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,360
At least in the past, the way you looked at me

119
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,960
was much more affectionate than how you looked at my brother.

120
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,840
You forgot you said

121
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:45,040
no one has ever cared about you like I do.

122
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,840
I cherish you more than my brother does,

123
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,240
and understand you better than him.

124
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,160
I didn't expect

125
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:54,000
the Second Young Master to be such a romantic.

126
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,960
You don't think I still have you

127
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,720
in my heart now, do you?

128
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,040
I know that recently,

129
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,800
there has been a lot of friction between us.

130
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,720
But I hope you understand

131
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,120
my heart hasn't changed.

132
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:06,240
As long as you're willing to wait,

133
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,040
I won't forget my past promises.

134
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,520
Let this glass of wine

135
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,040
serve to

136
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,650
untie the knots of our past.

137
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:13,920
How about it?

138
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,880
Mrs. Zhang,

139
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,880
why isn't the Second Young Master back yet?

140
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,880
I didn't see him.

141
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:22,810
First Young Master.

142
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,700
Why are you looking for Lu Jingxi?

143
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,440
First Young Master.

144
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,760
I... I wasn't looking for the Second Young Master.

145
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:30,080
I was just asking.

146
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,920
Where is the Young Madam?

147
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,080
Young Madam.

148
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,120
These are freshly pickled plums from the kitchen.

149
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,920
I brought them up for you to taste.

150
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:38,880
I'll eat later.

151
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:41,080
Young Madam, are you going out?

152
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:43,880
What's wrong?

153
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:47,200
Are you going to meet the Second Young Master?

154
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,880
What do you mean by a date?

155
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:51,520
He just said he wants to talk to me about some things.

156
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,600
It's not convenient at home.

157
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,960
I'm just going to have a meal.

158
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,960
Don't make it sound like I'm having an affair.

159
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,200
Young Madam, I'm sorry.

160
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,480
I didn't mean that.

161
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,960
I just feel...

162
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,800
What if the Eldest Young Master finds out?

163
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,320
Will he be unhappy?

164
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,560
He comes back so late every day.

165
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,600
How would he know?

166
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,920
You won't say anything, and I won't say anything.

167
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:08,720
Be smart.

168
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:10,720
But what if?

169
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,240
There are no what-ifs.

170
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,480
If there is, it's just him being angry on purpose.

171
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,080
It's none of my business.

172
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,640
There are no what-ifs.

173
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,760
There are no what-ifs. There are no what-ifs.

174
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:16,620
If I say there isn't, there isn't.

175
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,900
Find out where Lu Jingxi is right now.

176
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,520
Does the Second Young Master still remember his past promises?

177
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,380
I won't forget.

178
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,040
You want to settle abroad.

179
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,400
My oldest brother can't do that.

180
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,000
He can't let go of his status,

181
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,760
but I can.

182
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:38,520
Isn't that how we started?

183
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,800
Shen Zhixia,

184
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,800
so you really wanted to escape from here,

185
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,860
and that's why you got with Lu Jingxi.

186
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,960
I'll accept your promise for now.

187
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:51,360
But whether we can bury the hatchet

188
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,800
depends on what happens next.

189
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:56,700
A glass of wine alone can't settle it.

190
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,000
Sister-in-law.

191
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,260
Good evening, you two.

192
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:02,520
Our restaurant is collecting customer feedback.

193
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:03,560
Could I trouble you, sir,

194
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:05,360
to fill out a food feedback form?

195
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,120
After filling it out,

196
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:08,080
you can participate in our lucky draw.

197
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,120
Who let you in?

198
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,960
I asked her to come.

199
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:15,440
You want me to wait, Second Young Master.

200
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,240
That's fine.

201
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,160
But I also want to see

202
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,640
how your luck is.

203
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:21,240
And see if I can share in your good fortune.

204
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,160
Sure.

205
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:08,400
I am really sorry, sir.

206
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,800
You didn't win this time.

207
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:11,400
Better luck next time.

208
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:17,280
It seems Mr. Lu's luck isn't very good.

209
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:21,360
No wonder the good things in the Lu family never fall to you.

210
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:23,600
Shen Zhixia.

211
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:25,880
Are you so sure

212
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:28,680
that the Lu family's position will always belong to my older brother?

213
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:29,560
Lu Jingxi.

214
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,000
Are you so sure

215
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,460
that I care about your Lu family's business?

216
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,240
Shen Zhixia.

217
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,600
Do you really think

218
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:38,460
my older brother cares about you?

219
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,000
Let me tell you,

220
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,440
when Lu Jingheng thinks

221
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:43,170
you are no longer useful to him,

222
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:45,440
he will discard you like trash.

223
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,600
My business with him

224
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:49,570
is none of your concern, Second Young Master.

225
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,610
There are some things that,

226
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,760
even if you forget,

227
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:56,770
someone will remember for you.

